      "text": "At O’Hare last week, a passenger from Liberia was referred to AG Secondary to have their bags x-rayed. Some anomalies were identified &amp; AG Specialists examined the luggage &amp; found over 2lbs of porcupine meat. The meat was denied entry due to human health concerns &amp; destroyed. https://t.co/QCLIwZQLu3",
